      "side": 1,
      "message": "I agree that it is confusing, but it\u0027s a somewhat hard requirement for automatic scraping as implemented in https://review.openstack.org/#/c/401413/\n\nThe simplest ways around this I can see are:\n\n* (1) We could add monasca-specific configuration options to our  prometheus client plugin that would allow us to provide an alternate scrape path in k8s metadata. This would break compatibility with other Prometheus-compatible scrapers\n* (2) We keep it as-is and document the ambiguity\n\nA possible option #3 would be to offload metric serving to another external component. This would solve a number of other issues but has some major complexity penalties. Still something we are investigating :)",
